snippet.title: Horror Office: Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
🎮Play Horror Office: https://yahaha-horror.itch.io/horror-office

Game Intro: As you open your eyes, it's already deep into the night, and once again, you find yourself waking up in the office due to overtime work. But tonight is different.
Wait! There's a rabbit wielding a knife, seemingly intent on ending your life. Now, you must use anything you can find to escape the confines of the office!
Can you outsmart the menacing rabbit and uncover the dark secrets hidden within the office walls? 


Create your own horror game with the YAHAHA Horror Game Kit. 
🔥Try out Horror Game Kit🔥
 https://yahaha.com/horror-template?utm_source=Youtube
